[GRUNTING]

38
00:04:12.217 --> 00:04:13.114
Clyde!

39
00:04:15.013 --> 00:04:15.945
Yes. Owen.

40
00:04:16.083 --> 00:04:17.878
I'm gonna ask you kindly

41
00:04:19.293 --> 00:04:21.157
