155
00:13:08.097 --> 00:13:10.962
[ENGINE RUMBLING]

156
00:13:22.146 --> 00:13:24.838
[ENGINE RUMBLING]

157
00:13:28.738 --> 00:13:31.638
["MOONLIGHT SONATA" CONTINUES]

158
00:13:41.993 --> 00:13:44.547
